{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回\"扑朔迷离\"中，裴珏女扮男装随冷大叔骑马奔行，至一家客栈投宿。冷大叔实为女扮男装的武林高手冷月仙子艾青，她误将裴珏认作女子。入房后艾青更衣露出女儿身，裴珏不得已坦白自己是男子，艾青大怒欲废其武功，但见裴珏目光纯真而迟疑。裴珏讲述身世后，艾青心生同情，收其为徒。深夜，北斗七煞之三莫西色胆包天闯入房中，被艾青以桌角为暗器击退。艾青追至屋顶施展绝顶轻功戏弄莫西，莫西惊骇万分。本章揭开艾青真实身份，交代其与千手书生夫妻反目的往事，并引入北斗七煞这一新势力。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你是个女儿家，做事要谨慎些，以后在没有学会武功之前，千万不要出去一人乱跑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "今天你随便就跟着我走，这幸好是我，如果换了别人，那你难免又要吃亏。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "我——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "不要多说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "以后在外面，你就叫我冷大叔好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你会骑马？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "客官敢情是要房间吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "夫人怎地还不进来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敝店全客满了，只剩下一间房，两位就将就着住下吧，那里还算干净。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "text": "好吧，快带我们去。",
      "tone": "不耐烦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "快脱衣服休息，明天我们还要一早赶路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你不好意思是不是？等一会你就知道没关系了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你现在该知道我刚才所说的话的意思了吧，我其实不是男的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我要是个男的，你岂不是又要倒霉了吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我和你真有缘，一看见你，就觉得你孤苦伶仃，受人欺负，怪可怜的，所以才收你做徒弟，你别以为这么简单，恐怕以后你说给别人听，别人也不会相信呢了",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你不要奇怪，我从小就是这样睡觉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你多大了，怎地这样害臊？快脱衣裳睡呀，你看见我也是女的，还怕什么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "冷大——大叔，你快穿上——我——我是个男人。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "我是个男人，我——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷大叔",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你是找死，敢欺负姑奶奶！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "今天我若不让你痛快，我就不叫冷月仙子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你到底是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你别难受，我的身世也和你差不多，你并不笨，只要肯用心，将来武功也许比我还好，这以后慢慢再说吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快睡吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "冷——冷大叔，你累了，还是先睡吧，我到门外站站，反正天已快亮了。",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是你们，敢情你们活得真不耐烦了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你看看这个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "你知道这是谁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你留意看，这颗星可有什么古怪之处？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "对了，这就是江湖上声名最恶的七个人所留下的表记，哼！他们找到我，也是他们霉运到了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "他们是谁？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "他们是义结兄弟七人，自称为\"北斗七煞\"，平日无恶不做，武功想也不坏，别的事不说，这七煞里的老三和老七，最是好色——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "刚刚我看那图形，较大的一角，是由上往下数的第——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你记得第几个角较大吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "正是第三个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "这图形所示，是不是就是说这来的就是七煞中的老三呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "他来了，恐怕就再也走不掉了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "他留下了记号，是不是就一定会来呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "来是一定会来的，只不过不知道是什么时候罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别的不说，今夜我看来觉是无法睡的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_ai_qing",
      "text": "是不是已经来了？",
      "tone": "紧张",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你背过身子去，我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "不要动，也不要说话，已经快来了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "艾青",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你怕吗？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_xi",
      "speaker_name": "莫西",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "房里的可是道上同源，兄弟莫西，是合字，也请亮个万儿。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_xi",
      "speaker_name": "莫西",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友是何方神圣，再不开口，可别怪兄弟要不客气了。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_mo_xi",
      "text": "凭你也配问姑奶奶的名字。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_qing",
      "speaker_name": "冷月仙子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你等一会，我马上就来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    }
  ],
